---
interface Props {
  className?: string;
}

const { className = "" } = Astro.props;
---


<section class={`py-24 ${className}`}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        DEMO - Projects</h2>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">

        Interested in contributing to AI for Good? Get in touch and see how you can get involved. Whether you're a developer, designer, or just passionate about making a difference, there's a place for you in our community. Join us in harnessing the power of AI to create positive change in the world.
        Check out the <a href="https://github.com/cknzraposo/ai4gdpublic" class="text-teal-500 hover:underline">AI for Good GitHub repository</a> for more information on how to contribute, collaborate, and innovate with us. Together, we can build a better future through technology and creativity.
      </p>
    </div>

</section>